Interface UMLStereotype

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, com.mia.openapi.MIAEvaluableObject, com.mia.openapi.MIAObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, UMLGeneralizableElement, UMLMIAObject, UMLModelElement, UMLStereotype
public interface UMLStereotype
extends UMLGeneralizableElement, UMLStereotype

A representation of the model object 'UML Stereotype'.

The following features are supported:

  • Extended Elements
  • Icon
  • Base Class
  • Required Tags
  • Defined Tags
  • Stereotype Constraints
